Package: flights
Type: Package
Title: Information on Flights
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Heather
Maintainer: Heather <heather.summers@alumni.ubc.ca>
Description: This package includes functions that can be used to get information on flights including whether the departure or arrival delays are typically too long, provides the fuel usage per flight, and converts the flight distance from mile to kilometres. This package is best used in conjunction with the package `nycflights13`.
